{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":917,"text":"Guatemala is recovering from\na 36-year armed conflict."},{"time":4085,"text":"A conflict that was fought\nduring the Cold War."},{"time":6616,"text":"It was really just \na small leftist insurgency"},{"time":10669,"text":"and a devastating response by the state."},{"time":13836,"text":"What we have as a result\nis 200,000 civilian victims,"},{"time":16678,"text":"160,000 of those\nkilled in the communities:"},{"time":20332,"text":"small children, men, women, \nthe elderly even."},{"time":24428,"text":"And then we have \nabout 40,000 others, the missing,"},{"time":27858,"text":"the ones we're still looking for today."},{"time":30178,"text":"We call them the Desaparecidos."}]},{"cues":[{"time":32738,"text":"Now, 83 percent of the victims \nare Mayan victims,"},{"time":35603,"text":"victims that are the descendants"},{"time":38008,"text":"of the original inhabitants of \nCentral America."},{"time":40744,"text":"And only about 17 percent are of \nEuropean descent."},{"time":44251,"text":"But the most important thing here is that"},{"time":46308,"text":"the very people who are supposed to \ndefend us, the police, the military,"},{"time":52329,"text":"are the ones that committed\nmost of the crimes."}]},{"cues":[{"time":56035,"text":"Now the families,\nthey want information."},{"time":59335,"text":"They want to know what happened."},{"time":60902,"text":"They want the bodies of their loved ones."},{"time":63092,"text":"But most of all,\nwhat they want is they want you,"},{"time":66339,"text":"they want everyone to know\nthat their loved ones did nothing wrong."}]},{"cues":[{"time":71515,"text":"Now, my case was that my father\nreceived death threats in 1980."},{"time":77203,"text":"And we left."},{"time":78583,"text":"We left Guatemala and we came here."},{"time":80337,"text":"So I grew up in New York,"},{"time":81543,"text":"I grew up in Brooklyn as a matter of fact,\nand I went to New Utrecht High School"},{"time":85323,"text":"and I graduated from Brooklyn College."},{"time":87141,"text":"The only thing was that"},{"time":88707,"text":"I really didn't know what \nwas happening in Guatemala."},{"time":92578,"text":"I didn't care for it; it was too painful."},{"time":95447,"text":"But it wasn't till 1995 that I decided\nto do something about it."},{"time":99754,"text":"So I went back."},{"time":100908,"text":"I went back to Guatemala, \nto look for the bodies,"},{"time":104488,"text":"to understand what happened\nand to look for part of myself as well."}]},{"cues":[{"time":110051,"text":"The way we work is that\nwe give people information."},{"time":113414,"text":"We talk to the family members\nand we let them choose."},{"time":116384,"text":"We let them decide to tell\nus the stories,"},{"time":119614,"text":"to tell us what they saw,"},{"time":121466,"text":"to tell us about their loved ones."},{"time":123594,"text":"And even more important,"},{"time":124880,"text":"we let them choose to\ngive us a piece of themselves."},{"time":128878,"text":"A piece, an essence, of who they are."},{"time":131354,"text":"And that DNA is what we're \ngoing to compare"},{"time":133611,"text":"to the DNA that comes\nfrom the skeletons."}]},{"cues":[{"time":136331,"text":"While we're doing that, though,\nwe're looking for the bodies."},{"time":139386,"text":"And these are skeletons by now,"},{"time":141374,"text":"most of these crimes \nhappened 32 years ago."},{"time":144280,"text":"When we find the grave,"},{"time":145526,"text":"we take out the dirt and eventually clean \nthe body, document it, and exhume it."},{"time":149656,"text":"We literally bring the \nskeleton out of the ground."}]},{"cues":[{"time":153095,"text":"Once we have those bodies, though,\nwe take them back to the city, to our lab,"},{"time":157237,"text":"and we begin a process of trying\nto understand mainly two things:\n"},{"time":160321,"text":"One is how people died."},{"time":162614,"text":"So here you see a gunshot\nwound to the back of the head"},{"time":165718,"text":"or a machete wound, for example."},{"time":168367,"text":"The other thing we want to understand\nis who they are."},{"time":171693,"text":"Whether it's a baby,"},{"time":175152,"text":"or an adult."},{"time":176809,"text":"Whether it's a woman or a man."},{"time":178949,"text":"But when we're done\nwith that analysis"},{"time":180732,"text":"what we'll do is we'll take a small \nfragment of the bone"},{"time":183458,"text":"and we'll extract DNA from it."},{"time":186272,"text":"We'll take that DNA"},{"time":187367,"text":"and then we'll compare it with the\nDNA of the families, of course."}]},{"cues":[{"time":192127,"text":"The best way to explain this to you\nis by showing you two cases."},{"time":195771,"text":"The first is the case \nof the military diary."},{"time":198318,"text":"Now this is a document that was smuggled\nout of somewhere in 1999."},{"time":202993,"text":"And what you see there\nis the state following individuals,"},{"time":207673,"text":"people that, like you, \nwanted to change their country,"},{"time":211604,"text":"and they jotted everything down."},{"time":214484,"text":"And one of the things that they wrote \ndown is when they executed them."},{"time":218734,"text":"Inside that yellow rectangle, \nyou see a code,"},{"time":221715,"text":"it's a secret code: 300."},{"time":224026,"text":"And then you see a date."},{"time":225523,"text":"The 300 means \"executed\" and the date \nmeans when they were executed."},{"time":229196,"text":"Now that's going to come\ninto play in a second."},{"time":233064,"text":"What we did is we conducted\nan exhumation in 2003,"},{"time":236689,"text":"where we exhumed 220 bodies\nfrom 53 graves in a military base."},{"time":242640,"text":"Grave 9, though, matched the family\nof Sergio Saul Linares."},{"time":246635,"text":"Now Sergio was a professor\nat the university."},{"time":249361,"text":"He graduted from Iowa State University"},{"time":251752,"text":"and went back to Guatemala\nto change his country."},{"time":254129,"text":"And he was captured on \nFebruary 23, 1984."},{"time":258003,"text":"And if you can see there, he was \nexecuted on March 29, 1984,"},{"time":262092,"text":"which was incredible."},{"time":263658,"text":"We had the body, we had the family's \ninformation and their DNA,"},{"time":266680,"text":"and now we have documents\nthat told us exactly what happened."}]},{"cues":[{"time":270026,"text":"But most important is about\ntwo weeks later,"},{"time":273129,"text":"we go another hit, another match"},{"time":275816,"text":"from the same grave to Amancio Villatoro."},{"time":280617,"text":"The DNA of that body\nalso matched the DNA of that family."},{"time":283363,"text":"And then we noticed\nthat he was also in the diary."},{"time":286732,"text":"But it was amazing to see that he was \nalso executed on March 29, 1984."},{"time":291903,"text":"So that led us to think, hmm, \nhow many bodies were in the grave?"},{"time":296226,"text":"Six."},{"time":297413,"text":"So then we said, how many people\nwere executed on March 29, 1984?"},{"time":306716,"text":"That's right, six as well."},{"time":309034,"text":"So we have Juan de Dios, Hugo,\nMoises and Zoilo."},{"time":314726,"text":"All of them executed on the same date, \nall captured at different locations"},{"time":318574,"text":"and at different moments."},{"time":320328,"text":"All put in that grave."},{"time":321492,"text":"The only thing we needed now\nwas the DNA of those four families"},{"time":324636,"text":"So we went and we looked for them\nand we found them."},{"time":327881,"text":"And we identified those six bodies\nand gave them back to the families."}]},{"cues":[{"time":332344,"text":"The other case I want to tell you about"},{"time":334783,"text":"is that of a military base \ncalled CREOMPAZ."},{"time":338871,"text":"It actually means, \"to believe in peace,\"\nbut the acronym really means"},{"time":343482,"text":"Regional Command Center\nfor Peacekeeping Operations."},{"time":346501,"text":"And this is where the Guatemalan military\ntrains peacekeepers from other countries,"},{"time":351491,"text":"the ones that serve with the U.N."},{"time":354332,"text":"and go to countries\nlike Haiti and the Congo."},{"time":357095,"text":"Well, we have testimony that said that\nwithin this military base,"},{"time":360608,"text":"there were bodies, there were graves."},{"time":362713,"text":"So we went in there with a search warrant\nand about two hours after we went in,"},{"time":366568,"text":"we found the first of 84 graves, \na total of 533 bodies."},{"time":372192,"text":"Now, if you think about that,"},{"time":374829,"text":"peacekeepers being trained\non top of bodies."},{"time":378166,"text":"It's very ironic."}]},{"cues":[{"time":381545,"text":"But the bodies -- face down, most of them,\nhands tied behind their backs,"},{"time":386802,"text":"blindfolded, all types of trauma --"},{"time":389426,"text":"these were people who were defenseless\nwho were being executed."},{"time":392505,"text":"People that 533 families are looking for."},{"time":396530,"text":"So we're going to focus on Grave 15."},{"time":399142,"text":"Grave 15, what we noticed,\nwas a grave full of women and children,"},{"time":402838,"text":"63 of them."},{"time":405041,"text":"And that immediately made us think,"},{"time":408269,"text":"my goodness, where is there\na case like this?"},{"time":410544,"text":"When I got to Guatemala in 1995,"},{"time":413237,"text":"I heard of a case of a massacre\nthat happened on May 14, 1982,"},{"time":417888,"text":"where the army came in, killed the men,"},{"time":421021,"text":"and took the women and children \nin helicopters to an unknown location."},{"time":426026,"text":"Well, guess what?"},{"time":426968,"text":"The clothing from this grave matched the \nclothing from the region"},{"time":431161,"text":"where these people were taken from,"},{"time":432891,"text":"where these women and children \nwere taken from."}]},{"cues":[{"time":435274,"text":"So we conducted some DNA analysis,\nand guess what?"},{"time":438767,"text":"We identified Martina Rojas \nand Manuel Chen."},{"time":441034,"text":"Both of them disappeared in that case,\nand now we could prove it."},{"time":444109,"text":"We have physical evidence that\nproves that this happened"},{"time":447119,"text":"and that those people \nwere taken to this base."},{"time":449860,"text":"Now, Manuel Chen was three years old."},{"time":453118,"text":"His mother went to the river to wash \nclothes, and she left him with a neighbor."},{"time":457985,"text":"That's when the army came"},{"time":459689,"text":"and that's when he was taken away in \na helicopter and never seen again"},{"time":463029,"text":"until we found him in Grave 15."}]},{"cues":[{"time":465008,"text":"So now with science, with archaeology, \nwith anthropology, with genetics,"},{"time":470726,"text":"what we're doing is, we're\ngiving a voice to the voiceless."},{"time":473960,"text":"But we're doing more than that."},{"time":475645,"text":"We're actually providing \nevidence for trials,"},{"time":477810,"text":"like the genocide trial that happened \nlast year in Guatemala"},{"time":481332,"text":"where General RÃ­os Montt was found guilty\nof genocide and sentenced to 80 years."}]},{"cues":[{"time":486142,"text":"So I came here to tell you today\nthat this is happening everywhere --"},{"time":489787,"text":"it's happening in Mexico\nright in front of us today --"},{"time":492511,"text":"and we can't let it go on anymore."},{"time":494451,"text":"We have to now come together and decide"},{"time":497352,"text":"that we're not going to have \nany more missing."},{"time":499573,"text":"So no more missing, guys."},{"time":500765,"text":"Okay? No more missing."}]},{"cues":[{"time":503476,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":504719,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}